{"tid":1472051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海港城首席顧問吳光正原來係深藍","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T14:51:06.000Z","uid":56301,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b84033b748d55454c47b5b43d6c06b622b014cd","tid":1472051,"uid":56301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"之前海港城張貼「警方勿入」告示扮撐示威者，但係明報記者於8月12號已經見唔到相關告示。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1565610317829&amp;issue=20190812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1565610317829%26issue%3D20190812&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=1a55f0eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1565610317829%26issue%3D20190812&h=1080c43f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1565610317829&amp;issue=20190812</a><br />\n<br />\n而海港城為九倉旗下商場之一，九倉首席顧問吳光正有以下言論：<br />\n<br />\n《吳光正形容特首是百分百香港兒女　應支持她依法施政》<br />\n<br />\n九龍倉首席顧問吳光正，以「後反送中，出師無名，五求運動，無中生有」在報章撰文。<br />\n<br />\n吳光正提到，「反送中」訴求是今次運動的大樹，這個唯一的大訴求已獲政府於7月9日接納，政題大樹已倒，無論是否滿意「壽終正寢」這四個字也好，所有人都知道，「送中條例」已死。今時、將來的特首也不會重提。<br />\n<br />\n吳光正說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現時五求運動只是讓人感到是偽裝以「反送中」過氣的旗幟，去爭取「佔中」失敗未能得到的東西，又指這次與中央爭權、改《基本法》、改8.31定案，逼出政改使反對派能掌控立法會，似乎這些才是現在仍不收手的陰謀和最終目標。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n吳光正說，再這樣下去不會有贏家，後果也像5年前佔中一樣得個零，這次最後敗因也沒有變，不服氣，再與中央爭權，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以為這次可以用暴力去逼北京改《基本法》和8.31，他呼籲不要再令香港再付出沉重代價。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n他批評，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有不少想表達中立的人士和團體向特首林鄭月娥提出如何妥協，卻隻字不提反對暴力，令人失望，又指特首從沒有私心，是百分之百香港兒女，無功也有勞，應該支持她依法施政。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474118-20190812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474118-20190812.htm&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=dea9ac09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474118-20190812.htm&h=94a5d3c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474118-20190812.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細版本：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20190812/s00022/1565594021128/%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AB%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D-%E4%BA%94%E6%B1%82%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E5%90%B3%E5%85%89%E6%AD%A3%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20190812%2Fs00022%2F1565594021128%2F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25A3%25EF%25BC%2589&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=fc5442bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20190812%2Fs00022%2F1565594021128%2F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25A3%25EF%25BC%2589&h=9a0a865a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20190812/s00022/1565594021128/%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AB%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D-%E4%BA%94%E6%B1%82%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E5%90%B3%E5%85%89%E6%AD%A3%EF%BC%89</a><br />\n<br />\n九倉旗下商場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SA9NQTS.jp